{"tid":1631593,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[團結求共識] 停止裝修黨鐵, 建制派, 黑社會以外店鋪OK?","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:52:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T08:25:17.000Z","uid":71428,"like":15,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0cdd09b88538084ae649a0691f4827bef761ab49","tid":1631593,"uid":71428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:52:34.000Z","msg":"我地首先要重奪屬於市民既鐵路, 加強返我地既機動性, 同時削弱敵人既機動性<br />\n我地要同黨鐵講數, 承諾以下條件就停火, 若果再次出賣示威者就後果自負<br />\n1. 唔准再因公眾活動關站<br />\n2. 唔准關站運警<br />\n3. 唔准無故取消列車班次<br />\n4. 公開831 CCTV<br />\n<br />\n建制派同黑社會因為抵撚死成日搞搞震, 所以可以隨便裝修<br />\n其他店鋪都應該跟返獅鳥守則, 人不犯我我不犯人<br />\n中資係要理, 但唔係依家, 我地拎到想要既野,到時點玩都得"},{"pid":"cc7d8b48c4328daa16e0c94d12e8dcd423fa7529","tid":1631593,"uid":71428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:54:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5119029e74d0bda4c551197ee7e050010c7cfcb2","tid":1631593,"uid":71428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:55:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0e734c7e60b9514a26ef3b8d3b8bc3bab6f84e83","tid":1631593,"uid":71428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:56:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0796efde3efdf6b18fbd9b76c2459d1fcbf028d6","tid":1631593,"uid":71428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:56:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8ef6da523a7bd182e83081e26d78e9503864ba1d","tid":1631593,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:56:43.000Z","msg":"同意，裝修行動要停一陣（我冇話壽終正寢）<br />\n【地方的手足需要進化】麻煩大家入黎溫下書，睇下烏克蘭係E個時候做左D咩<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631278\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631278</a>"},{"pid":"82d0ca311fb38cc6f8925ca27700df5644b96027","tid":1631593,"uid":71428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:57:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"848cd905601ee8e048452420fb6b32e329afc27a","tid":1631593,"uid":175091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:58:20.000Z","msg":"對準十八區既政權標誌 做好文宣好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n14年係因為大台輸<br />\n19年我地要自省進化 人不犯我我不犯人<br />\n唔好因爲自己輸<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9dj9KVJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9dj9KVJ.png&h=ade45c84&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"586508a621aedac827c8ca4e6af1ccde286ee02d","tid":1631593,"uid":75959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:58:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">大家 呢幾日都係行動日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但連登都無比大陸DDos攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就證明左係大量五毛做緊野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又分化又風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地係時候要醒下<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰<br />\n<br />\n跟住就係開始做正經野：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 推紅色的士撞人單野<br />\n<br />\n2.推黑警又當街踢人單野<br />\n<br />\n3.九龍塘軍營入面有綠色防暴警既片<br />\n<br />\n4.解釋返裝修既原因比外國知<br />\n<br />\n5.宣傳黑紅藍黃既概念<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地唔好再比五毛搞爆連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"24720480816307b7ff3ee1fca0c9b0b326263572","tid":1631593,"uid":138097,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:59:31.000Z","msg":"唔OK 中資一定要搞"},{"pid":"15b4c8644f1f78458adf795d3c821ed3d3f3cd3d","tid":1631593,"uid":71428,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"24720480816307b7ff3ee1fca0c9b0b326263572","tid":1631593,"uid":138097,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":